  "texts": [
    "Finally, we combined the gene-specific Z-statistics in each pathway P as Eq.",
    "which follows a standard normal distribution under the null hypothesis.",
    "U373 RAD18 +/+ and U373 RAD18 -/-cells were infected with lentiCRISPR virus targeting the MLH1 gene, or with a lentivirus encoding a nontargeting control sgRNA.",
    "Stably transduced cells were selected in puromycin (2 µg/ml).",
    "Pools of the resulting U373 cells (RAD18 +/+ MLH1 +/+, RAD18 +/+ MLH1 -/-, RAD18 -/-MLH1 +/+, and RAD18 -/-MLH1 -/-) were seeded into 10 cm plates (5 × 10 5 cells/plate) and cultured in the presence of 4 µM TMZ (or DMSO for control groups) for 20 population doublings (PD20)."
